{"tid":614000,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人遇過呢種幻覺？","createTime":"2018-04-02T07:01:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-02T14:42:36.000Z","uid":167330,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e1f4b78cb02f9f96a08dfa0ed7d13136d62ff050","tid":614000,"uid":167330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T07:01:20.000Z","msg":"細個嗰陣（幼稚園）有日起身，突然見到好多半透明嘅卡通人物起我身邊，有大有細<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個數量係多到充斥起我見到嘅成個空間，而佢地係會受我嘅行為影響，例如我見到一個好細嘅蝙蝠俠起枱面跑緊，我放啲野起佢前面佢會識得跨過去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，用手打佢佢會跌低。情況就好似玩緊vr咁，但係同實境融合咗。<br />\n<br />\n個情況應該持續咗成個星期，嗰陣冇做過啲咩，淨係嗰日起得特別早身。雖然嗰陣時唔驚，但而家諗番起都好想知究竟係咩幻覺同埋點導致<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，有冇人都遇過啲解釋唔到嘅幻覺？"},{"pid":"77721e82c3736a9876f2d66eb434eee51dba3545","tid":614000,"uid":143686,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T12:53:01.000Z","msg":"發撚神經"},{"pid":"2347e0e912b603baecaf9aeeb4d343ca0b57610c","tid":614000,"uid":167330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"77721e82c3736a9876f2d66eb434eee51dba3545","tid":614000,"uid":143686,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T12:53:01.000Z","msg":"發撚神經"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T12:58:07.000Z","msg":"好認真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 冇吹水"},{"pid":"ebcd9be133df6aae6be1cd692a035bcba046a346","tid":614000,"uid":108756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"77721e82c3736a9876f2d66eb434eee51dba3545","tid":614000,"uid":143686,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T12:53:01.000Z","msg":"發撚神經"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T12:59:36.000Z","msg":"你又點知無可能/唔係真既？"},{"pid":"88a063dd14d8ba00ae9e1b7032fe080a17c30873","tid":614000,"uid":52719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T14:21:09.000Z","msg":"係岩岩訓醒個d時候?"},{"pid":"72904de337d9b37ee98a6151794ede767c0d5812","tid":614000,"uid":167330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"88a063dd14d8ba00ae9e1b7032fe080a17c30873","tid":614000,"uid":52719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T14:21:09.000Z","msg":"係岩岩訓醒個d時候?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T14:42:36.000Z","msg":"嗰日我應該五點左右就俾人叫醒咗（平時都瞓到8、9點）去屋企人出去，然後就開始出現呢啲幻覺，唔知關唔關事。"}]}